<br>
Want a 'cute' name? Plenty of other servers to choose from.<br>
<br>
It's a pain for guides to deal with petitions about name violations? Maybe if there was someone preemptively going after them, they wouldn't pile up in the petition queue.<br>
<br>
There are a lot of sucky things about being a guide. Fixing people's names sucks, and it's part of the job. Granted, it shouldn't take priority over tracking down bugs and locating corpses outside the world geometry, but it still needs to be done, especially on this server. <br>
